<text id="WB_KL-76">
    <metadata>
        <title>"The Sweathouse"</title>
        <author>Julia <alph>Starritt</alph></author>
        <date>1957</date>
        <publication>William Bright, <em>The Karok Language</em> (1957), pp. 288-289, Text
            76</publication>
    </metadata>
    <data>
        <paragraph>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w gl="the sweathouse"><m id="4407">p</m><m id="1826">eekmaháchraam</m></w>
                    <w><m id="6307">uum</m></w>
                    <w><m id="7096">yíth</m></w>
                    <w gl="it was made in some way"><m id="6175">u</m><m id="4004">kup</m><m
                            id="2348">eekyâa</m><m id="4004">hi</m><m id="6035">ti</m></w>
                    <w><m id="3752">káru</m></w>
                    <w gl="the living-house"><m id="4407">p</m><m id="2032">eekrívraam</m></w>
                    <w><m id="6307">uum</m></w>
                    <w><m id="6675">vúra</m></w>
                    <w><m id="7096">yith</m></w>. </kar>
                <eng>The sweathouse was made one way and the living-house another.</eng>
            </s>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w gl="the sweathouse"><m id="4407">p</m><m id="1826">eekmaháchraam</m></w>
                    <w><m id="6307">uum</m></w>
                    <w><m id="5502">sú'</m></w>
                    <w gl="it was dug into"><m id="6175">u</m><m id="2914">'íripkurih</m><m id="168"
                            >ahi</m><m id="6035">tih</m></w>. </kar>
                <eng>The sweathouse was dug down into the ground.</eng>
            </s>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w><m id="6847">xás</m></w>
                    <w><m id="3444">iv'ávahkam</m></w>
                    <w><m id="6675">vúra</m></w>
                    <w gl="wide boards"><m id="1719">ivhara</m><m id="6087">tírih</m><m id="5200"
                            >shas</m></w>
                    <w><m id="4281">mûuk</m></w>
                    <w gl="it was put up"><m id="6175">u</m><m id="3612">yururâa</m><m id="6380"
                            >na</m><m id="168">hi</m><m id="6035">tih</m></w>. </kar>
                <eng>And the roof was put up with wide boards.</eng>
            </s>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w><m id="6847">xás</m></w>
                    <w><m id="3292">ithváaykam</m></w>
                    <w gl="the door"><m id="4407">pa</m><m id="1187">chivchaksurúraam</m></w>
                    <w><m id="6675">vúra</m></w>
                    <w><m id="2810">ipshûunkinich</m></w>
                    <w gl="there"><m id="4408">pa</m><m id="3670">káan</m></w>
                    <w gl="they crawl into"><m id="3977">kun</m><m id="6612">vóonkurih</m><m
                            id="6379">vu</m><m id="6035">tih</m></w>. </kar>
                <eng>And in front, there was a low door, where they went in.</eng>
            </s>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w><m id="6847">xás</m></w>
                    <w><m id="6677">vuráakir</m></w>
                    <w gl="it stands"><m id="6175">u</m><m id="1646">'íihya</m></w>, <w><m id="6847"
                            >xás</m></w>
                    <w><m id="6381">vaa</m></w>
                    <w><m id="3670">káan</m></w>
                    <w gl="they crawl down to"><m id="4408">pa</m><m id="3977">kun</m><m id="6624"
                            >vóoruniih</m><m id="6379">vu</m><m id="6035">tih</m></w>. </kar>
                <eng>And a ladder stood (there), and they crawled down (into the house) on
                    that.</eng>
            </s>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w gl="the ladder"><m id="4407">pa</m><m id="6677">vuráakir</m></w>
                    <w><m id="6307">uum</m></w>
                    <w><m id="6675">vúra</m></w>
                    <w><m id="2682">ípaha</m></w>
                    <w gl="it was made with"><m id="4408">p</m><m id="6175">oo</m><m id="2336"
                            >kyâar</m><m id="168">ahi</m><m id="6035">tih</m></w>. </kar>
                <eng>The ladder was made of a tree.</eng>
            </s>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w><m id="6847">xás</m></w>
                    <w><m id="1671">iinâak</m></w>
                    <w gl="its floor"><m id="4407">pa</m><m id="4260">mu</m><m id="1694"
                        >'îirish</m></w>
                    <w><m id="6307">uum</m></w>
                    <w><m id="583">ás</m></w>
                    <w gl="it was covered with"><m id="6175">u</m><m id="4652">pathrív</m><m
                            id="168">ahi</m><m id="6035">tih</m></w>. </kar>
                <eng>And inside, their floor was covered with rocks.</eng>
            </s>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w><m id="6847">xás</m></w>
                    <w gl="middle of the floor"><m id="1694">irísh</m><m id="5">'aachip</m></w>
                    <w><m id="5502">sú'</m></w>
                    <w gl="a hole was made into"><m id="6175">u</m><m id="5486">súrukurih</m><m
                            id="168">ahi</m><m id="6035">tih</m></w>. </kar>
                <eng>And there was a hole in the middle of the floor.</eng>
            </s>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w><m id="6847">xás</m></w>
                    <w><m id="6383">vaa</m></w>
                    <w><m id="3670">káan</m></w>
                    <w gl="the fire"><m id="4407">pá</m><m id="10">'aah</m></w>
                    <w gl="they made"><m id="3977">kun</m><m id="2348">ikyâa</m><m id="6035"
                        >tih</m></w>. </kar>
                <eng>And they made the fire there.</eng>
            </s>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w><m id="6847">xás</m></w>
                    <w gl="one side"><m id="411">ápap</m><m id="3731">kam</m></w>
                    <w><m id="3752">káru</m></w>
                    <w gl="a hole was through"><m id="6175">u</m><m id="5488">súruruprin</m><m
                            id="168">ahi</m><m id="6035">tih</m></w>. </kar>
                <eng>And on the other side, there was also a hole through.</eng>
            </s>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w gl="when"><m id="4408">pa</m><m id="5506">tá</m></w>
                    <w gl="when they stop"><m id="3977">kun</m><m id="3909">kôo</m><m id="1358"
                            >haak</m></w>
                    <w><m id="1671">iinâak</m></w>
                    <w gl="staying"><m id="6376">v</m><m id="1975">éekrii</m></w>
                    <w><m id="6847">xás</m></w>
                    <w><m id="6383">vaa</m></w>
                    <w><m id="3670">káan</m></w>
                    <w><m id="5506">tá</m></w>
                    <w gl="they come outdoors"><m id="3977">kun</m><m id="6618">vôonupuk</m></w>. </kar>
                <eng>When they were finished staying inside, then they crawled out there.</eng>
            </s>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w><m id="6847">xás</m></w>
                    <w><m id="5328">sáruk</m></w>
                    <w><m id="4076">kúuk</m></w>
                    <w><m id="5506">tá</m></w>
                    <w gl="they arrive"><m id="3977">kun</m><m id="6306">'uum</m></w>, <w><m
                            id="6847">xás</m></w>
                    <w><m id="6337">úuth</m></w>
                    <w gl="in the river"><m id="3007">ishkêesh</m><m id="232">ak</m></w>
                    <w><m id="5506">tá</m></w>
                    <w gl="they bathe"><m id="3977">kun</m><m id="4443">páatva</m></w>. </kar>
                <eng>And they went downhill, and they bathed out in the river.</eng>
            </s>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w><m id="6847">xás</m></w>
                    <w gl="when"><m id="4408">pa</m><m id="5506">tá</m></w>
                    <w gl="when they sweat themselves"><m id="3977">kun</m><m id="4860"
                            >píkniihva</m><m id="1358">haak</m></w>, <w gl="the fire"><m id="4408"
                            >pá</m><m id="10">'aah</m></w>
                    <w><m id="5506">tá</m></w>
                    <w gl="they make"><m id="3977">kun</m><m id="2348">íkyav</m></w>, <w><m
                            id="6383">vaa</m></w>
                    <w gl="they use"><m id="3977">kun</m><m id="1584">íhruuv</m><m id="6035"
                        >ti</m></w>
                    <w gl="fir boughs"><m id="5568">tahpus</m><m id="459">'áptiik</m></w>. </kar>
                <eng>And when they sweated themselves, they made the fire, they used fir
                    boughs.</eng>
            </s>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w><m id="6847">xás</m></w>
                    <w><m id="6383">vaa</m></w>
                    <w><m id="2428">imfiráriik</m></w>
                    <w><m id="5506">tá</m></w>
                    <w gl="they make"><m id="3977">kun</m><m id="2348">íkyav</m></w>
                    <w><m id="6675">vúra</m></w>. </kar>
                <eng>And they made it a hot place.</eng>
            </s>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w><m id="6847">xás</m></w>
                    <w><m id="6675">vúra</m></w>
                    <w><m id="5156">puxích</m></w>
                    <w><m id="5506">tá</m></w>
                    <w gl="they get hot"><m id="3977">kun</m><m id="2406">ímchax</m></w>, <w><m
                            id="6847">xás</m></w>
                    <w><m id="5506">tá</m></w>
                    <w gl="they sweat"><m id="3977">kun</m><m id="710">ástuukha</m></w>. </kar>
                <eng>And it got very hot, and they sweated.</eng>
            </s>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w><m id="5163">púyava</m></w>
                    <w><m id="6847">xás</m></w>
                    <w><m id="3745">kári</m></w>
                    <w gl="when"><m id="4408">pa</m><m id="5506">tá</m></w>
                    <w gl="they rush outdoors"><m id="3977">kun</m><m id="569">'árihrupuk</m></w>. </kar>
                <eng>Then they rushed outside.</eng>
            </s>
        </paragraph>
    </data>
</text>
